"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/pct2rgb.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam je izveden iz `GDAL pct2rgb alatke "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/pct2rgb.html>`_."

