"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdal_polygonize.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam je izveden iz `GDAL polygonize alatke "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdal_polygonize.html>`_."

